"addo cyfrannu ati'."

#: pb/web/faq.php:43
msgid "How does it work?"
msgstr "Sut mae e'n gweithio?"

#: pb/web/faq.php:45
msgid ""
"PledgeBank allows users to set up pledges and then encourages other\n"
"people to sign up to them. A pledge is a statement of the form 'I will\n"
"do something, if a certain number of people will help me do it'. The\n"
"creator of the pledge then publicises their pledge and encourages\n"
"people to sign up. One of two possible outcomes is possible - either\n"
"the pledge fails to get enough subscribers before it expires. In that\n"
"case, we contact everyone and tell them 'better luck next time'. But\n"
"the better possibility is that a pledge attracts enough people that\n"
"they are all sent a message saying 'Well done - now get going!' "
msgstr ""
"Mae PledgeBank yn galluogi defnyddwyr i osod addewidion ac yna annog pobl\n"
"eraill i arwyddo'r addewid. Mae addewid yn osodiad mewn ffurf ''Dwi'n\n"
"fodlon gwneud rhywbeth, os yw rhif arbennig o bobl yn fodlon fy helpu'.\n"
"Bydd y sawl a greodd yr addewid yna'n hyrwyddo eu haddewid ac yn annog\n"
"pobl i arwyddo'r addewid. Mae un o ddau ganlyniad yn bosib - unai\n"
"bydd yr addewid yn methu cael digon o danysgrifiwyr cyn y dyddiad cau. Yn yr\n"
"achos hyn, byddwn yn cysylltu &acirc; phawb a dweud wrthynt 'gwell lwc tro \n"
"nesaf'. Ond gwell canlyniad yw pan fo addewid yn denu digon o bobl fel\n"
"bod pawb yn derbyn neges yn dweud 'da iawn - nawr ewch ati!' "

#: pb/web/faq.php:55
msgid "What can I ask people to pledge?"
msgstr "Beth allaf ofyn i bobl addewid?"

#: pb/web/faq.php:57
msgid ""
"Pretty much anything which isn't illegal, and which doesn't incite\n"
"people to commit illegal actions. Anything too obscene might also be\n"
"taken down - this is a family friendly site!"
msgstr ""
"Mwy neu lai unrhybweth nad yw'n anghyfreithlon, a sydd ddim yn ysgogi \n"
"pobl i gyflawni gweithredoedd anghyfreithlon. Bydd unrhywbeth sy'n rhy\n"
"anweddus hefyd yn cael ei ddileu - gwefan addas i'r teulu cyfan yw hwn!"

#: pb/web/faq.php:61
msgid "How can you be sure people will bother to carry out the pledge?"
msgstr "Sut allaf fod yn siwr y bydd pobl yn trafferthu gweithredu'r addewid?"

#: pb/web/faq.php:63
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We can't; PledgeBank is based on a psychological bet. We believe that\n"
"if a person possesses a slight desire to do something, and then we help\n"
"connect them to a bunch of  people who also want to do the same thing\n"
"then that first person is much more likely to act.  Update: we have now\n"
"surveyed a load of money based pledges that have succeeded, and found that\n"
"payment rates vary from 50% to well over 150%, with three-quarters of \n"
"people paying being typical."
msgstr ""
"Allwn ni ddim; mae PledgeBank yn seiliedig ar bet seicolegol. Rydym yn \n"
"credu os yw person yn meddu &acirc;'r awydd lleiaf i wneud rhywbeth, ac rydym yna'n\n"
"help eu cysylltu &acirc; chriw o bobl sydd eisiau gwenud yr un peth\n"
"yna mae'r person cyntaf yn fwy tebygol o weithredu. Dyfalwn y bydd hyn yn\n"
"gweithio'n dda iawn mewn rhai maesydd o weithgarwch a ddim o gwbl yn eraill\n"
" - dyna yw natur dynol."

#: pb/web/faq.php:71
msgid "What do I get out of it?"
msgstr "Neth ydw i'n gael allan ohono?"

#: pb/web/faq.php:73
msgid ""
"As a well intentioned subscriber, you get insurance against being the\n"
"only person to show up to the demo the freezing rain or against being\n"
"the parent who discovers they've just volunteered to run the entire\n"
"school play on their own. As a pledge creator - you get a greatly\n"
"improved chance of achieving whatever change it is you want."
msgstr ""
"Fel tanysgrifiwr gyda'r bwriad gorau, rydych yn cael yr yswiriant yn erbyn\n"
"bod yr unig berson sy'n mynychu gwrthdystiad yn y glaw oer neu yn erbyn bod\n"
"y rhiant sy'n sylweddoli eu bod newydd wirfoddoli i drefnu'r holl sioe\n"
"ysgol ar ben eu hunain. Fel creuwr addewid - mae ganddoch siawns llawer gwell\n"
"o wireddu pa bynnag newid rydych yn geisio ei gyflawni."

#: pb/web/faq.php:79
msgid "Is it free?"
msgstr "Ydy e yn rhad ac am ddim?"

#: pb/web/faq.php:81
